text: Jamie Leweling (born 26 February 2001) is a German professional footballer who plays as a midfielder for SpVgg Greuther Fürth. ==Career== Leweling made his professional debut for Greuther Fürth in the 2. Bundesliga on 28 July 2019, coming on as a substitute in the 85th minute for Tobias Mohr in the home match against Erzgebirge Aue, which finished as a 0–2 loss. ==References== ==External links== * * Profile at kicker.de Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:German footballers Category:Association football midfielders Category:SpVgg Greuther Fürth players Category:2.
